title: Joker - Silent Evil Pt. 1
description:
The first compilation of all the songs from 2007 and early 2008 by Joker. The series being released for free, "Silent Evil" refers to me being an unsigned rapper and having barely any plays going, and allot of twisted thoughts. I have these all copyrighted to Jesse "Joker" Rutledge. Enjoy!

2. Satan&#039;s Basement(ft. DC and Damaged)
3. Slither(ft. Samps and Korruption)
4. Terror
5. Used To be(ft. E&#039;l Kamurk)
6. We&#039;ll Drink On(ft. DC & SkarKrow)
7. In your Mind(ft. Samps)
